"This is the history of how [[Community Savings Pools]] came to be - an interview with Bryan Innes of New Zealand. The number of participants in the community wealth system has been doubling each year since 2011. For example the Lyttelton Harbour Pool went from about 8 members to 24 last year. There are over 20 pools in NZ as of January, 2014."


